T16TD4391E:319b-0: @319b `[?] // rgyal ba'i lam la 'jug pa las byung ba'i smon lam bzhugs /
T16TD4391E:319b-2: * // dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4391E:319b-3: rgyal ba'i lam 'jug yang dag par //
T16TD4391E:319b-4: sbyar las bsod nams tshad med gang //
T16TD4391E:319b-5: de yis 'gro kun rgyal ba yi //
T16TD4391E:319b-6: lam la legs par 'jug par shog / bdag gis bsod nams 'di yis ni //
T16TD4391E:319b-7: nam mkha' kun khyab skye bo rnams //
T16TD4391E:319b-8: ngan 'gro kun las nges grol zhing //
T16TD4391E:319b-9: mi khom thams cad rnam par spangs //
T16TD4391E:319b-10: skye ba lha dang mi yi ni //
T16TD4391E:319b-11: skye ba yongs su thob par shog / srid pa sdug bsngal gyis skrag pa //
T16TD4391E:319b-12: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro zhing //
T16TD4391E:319b-13: dam chos nyan sems don bsgom dang //
T16TD4391E:319b-14: sems ni dben par gnas par shog / theg pa chen po la gnas te //
T16TD4391E:319b-15: tshangs pa'i spyod dang ldan par shog / lam kun rnam par bsgom pa yis //
T16TD4391E:319b-16: sa la sogs pa kun thob nas //
T16TD4391E:319b-17: zhing kun yang dag sbyangs nas ni //
T16TD4391E:319b-18: myur du sangs rgyas thob par shog / ji ltar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs su //
T16TD4391E:319b-19: bsam pa'i don kun thams cad ni //
T16TD4391E:319b-20: nam mkha' mdzad bzhin mkha' nyid nas //
T16TD4391E:319b-21: sems can kun la 'byung bar shog /
T16TD4391E:320a-0: @320a * // phyogs bcu nam mkha'i mthar gnas pa'i //
T16TD4391E:320a-1: 'jig rten khams ni de dag rnams //
T16TD4391E:320a-2: don kun 'jig rten khams bzhin du //
T16TD4391E:320a-3: de ltar thams cad dag par shog / bdag kyang byang chub snying po'i bar //
T16TD4391E:320a-4: zang zing mi 'jigs dam chos dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-5: byams pas sems can thams cad kyi //
T16TD4391E:320a-6: bsam kun yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
T16TD4391E:320a-7: rtag pa nyid du tshangs spyod dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-8: sdom pa kun gyis bsdams par shog / sems can don kun byed pa dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-9: chos kun don ni ston par shog /'jig rten khams ni sems can kun //
T16TD4391E:320a-10: gang la gnod pa byed kyang ni //
T16TD4391E:320a-11: bdag ni de dag thams cad la //
T16TD4391E:320a-12: phan 'dogs byed pa nyid du shog /'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bsran nas bdag / rtag par sems can don brtson //
T16TD4391E:320a-13: sems ni dam chos bsam gtan la //
T16TD4391E:320a-14: ro gcig brtan pa nyid du shog / ji ltar brtson ldan brtson 'grus bzhin //
T16TD4391E:320a-15: bdag kyang go cha sbyar ba dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-16: de bzhin mi ldog pa zhes pa'i //
T16TD4391E:320a-17: brtson 'grus dang ni ldan par shog / ting 'dzin phun sum tshogs pa yi //
T16TD4391E:320a-18: tshogs kyi byang chub bsgrub pa yis //
T16TD4391E:320a-19: bsam gtan kun la gcig tu gnas //
T16TD4391E:320a-20: bdag sems rdo rje lta bur shog / shes rab nam mkha'i mtha' khyab pa //
T16TD4391E:320a-21: rdo rje yi ni mtshan nyid dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-22: rab mthun kun dga' tshogs dang ni //
T16TD4391E:320a-23: snying rje'i ro yis nges gang zhing //
T16TD4391E:320a-24: thabs dang smon lam de bzhin du //
T16TD4391E:320a-25: stobs ni rab tu sbyor ba dang //
T16TD4391E:320a-26: ye shes bdag nyid 'di dag ni //
T16TD4391E:320a-27: bdag la rnam par dag par shog / mngon shes kun gyi phar phyin te //
T16TD4391E:320a-28: khyad par lam ni thob par shog / sangs rgyas zhing ni rnam sbyang zhing //
T16TD4391E:320a-29: bdag ni sangs rgyas nyid gyur cig /'di nyid kyis ni rim pa yis //
T16TD4391E:320a-30: bdag gi bsod nams mthu yis ni //
T16TD4391E:320a-31: 'khor bar gnas pa'i sems can kun //
T16TD4391E:320a-32: myur du rgyal ba nyid du shog / bsod nams yongs su bsngo ba 'di //
T16TD4391E:320a-33: bdag nyid kyis ni blo yis byas //
T16TD4391E:320a-34: kun nas kun tu ma lus pa //
T16TD4391E:320a-35: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mkhyen pas na //
T16TD4391E:320a-36: kun du bzang po zhes bgyi ba'o //
T16TD4391E:320a-37: smon lam rgya mtsho ji lta ba //
T16TD4391E:320b-0: de bzhin @320b du ni bdag la yang //
T16TD4391E:320b-1: dge ba rgya mtsho de myur du //
T16TD4391E:320b-2: 'bras bu dang ni bcas par shog / phyogs bcu nam mkha' kun khyab pa'i //
T16TD4391E:320b-3: sangs rgyas zhing gi rgyal rnams shar //
T16TD4391E:320b-4: de dag ji ltar smon lam ni //
T16TD4391E:320b-5: sngon du byas pa'i rim pa rnams //
T16TD4391E:320b-6: de tsam nyid du bdag gis kyang //
T16TD4391E:320b-7: bsam pa brtan pa de bzhin bgyi //
T16TD4391E:320b-8: bsod nams mthu yis 'di dag ni //
T16TD4391E:320b-9: de bzhin du ni grub par shog / ji ltar dpal ldan 'jam dbyangs kyi //
T16TD4391E:320b-10: smon lam de bzhin bdag gis yang //
T16TD4391E:320b-11: dus ni yun mi ring ba yis //
T16TD4391E:320b-12: smon lam 'di ni rdzogs par shog / sangs rgyas kun rnams rang rang gi / zhing bzhugs mya ngan mi 'da' zhing //
T16TD4391E:320b-13: mkha' mnyam chos kyi char gyis ni //
T16TD4391E:320b-14: rtag tu sems can tshim byed shog / sems can rnams kyang sangs rgyas chos //
T16TD4391E:320b-15: dge 'dun bcas pa thams cad la //
T16TD4391E:320b-16: lha rdzas mchod sprin mtha' yas pas //
T16TD4391E:320b-17: yang dag par ni mchod byed shog / de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan gyis //
T16TD4391E:320b-18: 'jig rten khams kun gang bar shog / mchog gi chos rnams sems 'gyur zhing //
T16TD4391E:320b-19: srid pa sbyong bar byed par shog / pandi ta sangs gyas dpal ye shes kyis mdzad pa //
T16TD4391E:320b-20: rgyal ba'i lam la 'jug pa las byung ba'i smon lam rdzogs so//
